{{Infobox video game |title=Bear With Me |image=File:BearWithMeGameLogo.jpg |developer=[[Exordium Games]] |publisher=Exordium Games |engine=[[Unity Engine]] |director= |producer= |designer= |composer= |platforms=[[Microsoft Windows]],[[OSX]] |released= {{collapsible list|title=Episode One|'''Windows low-resolution'''{{vgrelease|NA|August 8, 2016}}}} {{collapsible list|title=Episode Two|'''Windows'''{{vgrelease|WW|February 15, 2017}}}} {{collapsible list|title=Episode Three|'''Windows'''{{vgrelease|WW|October 5, 2017}}}} |genre= [[Adventure game|Adventure]] |modes=[[Single-player]] }}
'''Bear With Me''' is a point n' click [[adventure game]] developed by [[Exordium Games]]. It is described as an "episodic noir adventure game", and was released in three episodes, first in August 2016, final in October 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/bear-with-me-a-noir-teddy-bear-adventure-concludes-in-october/|title=Bear With Me, a noir teddy bear adventure, concludes in October|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/07/21/bear-with-me/#more-384347|title=Bear With Me Investigates Plush Noir In August|date=21 July 2016|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goodgame.hr/ovog-listopada-zavrsavamo-slucaj-stize-treca-i-finalna-epizoda-bear-with-me/|title=Ovog listopada završavamo slučaj – stiže treća i finalna epizoda Bear with Me - GoodGame.hr|website=www.goodgame.hr}}</ref> The game draws inspiration from [[film noir]] and features Amber and her friend - detective Ted E. Bear, who are set on an adventure to find Amber's missing brother Flint.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.netokracija.com/druga-epizoda-bear-with-me-130781|title=2. epizoda igre Bear With Me zagrebačkog Exordium Gamesa stiže u veljači|date=20 January 2017|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2016/07/16/episodic-noir-adventure-game-bear-with-me-comes-out-on-august-8/217135/|title=Episodic Noir Adventure Game Bear With Me Comes Out on August 8 - Hardcore Gamer|website=www.hardcoregamer.com}}</ref> The game will also come on [[Nintendo Switch]] in Q2 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2018/02/noire_point-and-click_adventure_bear_with_me_is_heading_to_switch|title=Noire Point-And-Click Adventure Bear With Me Is Heading To Switch|first=Nintendo|last=Life|date=8 February 2018|publisher=}}</ref>
==Reception== {{VG Series Reviews |gr = no |game1 = Episode One |mc1 = (Windows) 68%<ref name=mone>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/bear-with-me-episode-1 |title=Bear With Me: Episode 1 PC Reviews at Metacritic |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-12-17}}</ref> |game2 = Episode Two |mc2 = (Windows) 76%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/bear-with-me-episode-two |title=Bear With Me: Episode Two PC Reviews at Metacritic |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-05-20}}</ref> |game3 = Episode Three |mc3 = (Windows) 79%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/bear-with-me-episode-three |title=Bear With Me: Episode Three PC Reviews at Metacritic |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=2018-02-24}}</ref> }}
Bear With Me received mixed to positive reviews. [[Adventure Gamers]], in a review for all three episodes, praised its story, art style and the well integration of puzzles, but criticized the slow movement speed, and the occasional frustration, giving it 3½ out of 5.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://adventuregamers.com/articles/view/31568|title=Bear With Me Review|website=Adventure Gamers}}</ref> Italian magazine [[The Games Machine (Italy)|The Games Machine]] gave it 7.9 out of 10, stating "Bear With Me is a nice, old-style point and click adventure, with logical and well designed puzzles, although not too challenging, and a story that blends humour and drama. Not a milestone in the genre, but adventure fans should give it a chance.".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thegamesmachine.it/bear-with-me/bear-with-me-recensione-pc/|title=Bear With Me Recensione PC - The Games Machine|publisher=}}</ref>
===Episode 1=== [[Hardcore Gamer]] was less positive in its review for the first episode of the series, arguing "The first episode of Bear With Me still hints at a greater game to come, nicely setting a proper noir tone with some occasional creepy bits and a gleeful dose of snark throughout.", but "it sadly says a lot that the initial outing feels more like a demo for the game than an actual full-fledged chapter of the story."<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hardcoregamer.com/2016/08/08/review-bear-with-me-episode-1/220075/|title=Review: Bear With Me: Episode 1 - Hardcore Gamer|website=www.hardcoregamer.com}}</ref> [[LeveL]] magazine, on the other hand, gave it 8/10 and praised it as "The first episode of a dark adventure, where childlike elements are mixed with an adult story in a perfect harmony of a noir story".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.level.cz/starsi-cisla/level-267/|title=LEVEL 267 - LEVEL|publisher=}}</ref><ref name=mone/>
